Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:52.67,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:54.96,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你就是…
Comment: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:31.32,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,正文
