Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是戰術嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,現在可不是拖拖拉拉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:02.25,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,全員 按照指示快速撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,指揮就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:08.17,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道了
