Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:41.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.90,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}停下！別四處亂跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,救救我…
